# .reviewguidesignore - Exclude review guides from discovery
# Uses gitignore syntax (patterns, wildcards, directory matches).
# Matching is done via: git check-ignore --no-index
#
# Examples:
#   general/performance.md    # Exclude a specific mode
#   android/                  # Exclude an entire category
#   *.draft.md                # Exclude all draft modes
#   !general/security.md      # Re-include after a broader exclusion
